---
---

<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-content animate-fade-up">
      <h2 class="section-title">The Kaveo Approach</h2>
      <div class="about-grid">
        <!-- Add Image Here -->
        <div class="about-image-wrapper animate-fade-up delay-100">
          <img src="/avatar.png" alt="Kaveo Remote Office" class="about-img" />
          <div class="img-overlay"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-content-wrapper animate-fade-up delay-200">
          <div class="about-text">
            <p>
              I don't run a massive corporate agency. When you work with Kaveo, you deal directly with me—the specialist building your lead-generation asset. No junior account managers, no jargon, and absolutely no bullshit.
            </p>
            <p>
              Just a hyper-focused partnership designed to make your phone ring. I specialize in Local SEO and high-conversion websites exclusively for tradies (plumbers, electricians, and landscapers).
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="stats-container">
            <div class="stat-card">
              <span class="stat-number">0</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Lock-in Contracts</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
              <span class="stat-number">100%</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Code Ownership</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 8rem 0;
    background-color: var(--color-dark-blue);
    color: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .about-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.8fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .about-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
  }

  /* Optional slight blue tint over the image to blend with the dark blue background */
  .img-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.2); /* Tint dark blue */
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .about-text {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(249, 246, 240, 0.85); /* Slightly muted cream */
  }

  .about-text p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .stats-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: rgba(249, 246, 240, 0.05);
    padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(249, 246, 240, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    background: rgba(249, 246, 240, 0.08);
  }

  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--color-accent-blue);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about {
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
    .stat-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
